data.description: Nestled in one of Wingfield Springs' most coveted neighborhoods, this charming residence awaits you. Set on a highly desirable oversized lot within the Bella Vista Subdivision. Benefit from proximity to essential amenities including grocery stores, restaurants, and The Red Hawk Golf course, all just a short distance away. The downstairs master suite ensures long-term comfort, while a centrally located half bath facilitates effortless entertaining. Upstairs, discover two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a generously sized loft overlooking the living area, enhancing the home's airy ambiance. The kitchen boasts a spacious pantry, kitchen nook, double ovens, gas cooktop, and center island with counter seating. With an oversized 2-car garage providing ample storage space, this home is poised to cater to your every need.
